<br>
a few common answers would be:<br>
<br>
to hang with friends and others from around the world to kick virtual ass!<br>
<br>
to chat with friends while playing an incredible 3D roleplaying game<br>
<br>
to power game and get the latest and greatest of all gear/items<br>
<br>
to be the first to do things, to explore new lands<br>
<br>
